  "text": "We think creating interfaces based on agent technology does not only follow the new paradigm of agentbased software development but leads to several advantages, too. O'Malley et al. list several guidelines whether an agent-oriented approach is useful [CITATION_1] . According to them agent-based graphical user interfaces can be necessary, because:",
